{
  "stem": "22463.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When you come back, you have, probably, the soup [INAUDIBLE] in mind.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You-- you have to have a showers over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Cold water.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was sitting in-- washing my-- not washing-- the-- I was always very-- I have some trouble with my feet.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- they [? have been ?] tired.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I have to put in the hot water and keep it for a while.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "By this-- for-- for-- that's-- that's what's happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was sitting outside my barrack, and with feet in my-- in the water.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All of a sudden, I-- I saw that something is running-- running from the-- from the air.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was-- later we find out there were-- there was a few days of-- or maybe the same day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because I [? don't ?] [? see ?] [? it anymore. ?] There was plenty of barracks, other.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And every-- everything in-- in a few minutes was in fire.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I [INAUDIBLE] and run to-- to-- girls' barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "To let-- to waken up and ask him to-- to go away, and run-- to run away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was a-- a-- not pilot, the sitting-- [INAUDIBLE] man, who was with a machine gun.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he-- he falled in a-- in middle of a-- between our barracks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was completely burned out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "According to the gossip, I couldn't-- I couldn't be sure.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The Allied forces had been bombarding Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a-- a synthetic factory of-- of petrol.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And probably he was shot over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then dismembered over the Cracow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably, as we later find out, there was Australian one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There is now, a-- a plaque in the factory above the door.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe that it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- of course, I couldn't prove it.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
